lead_paragraph: Russell Martin hit a long home run, AL MVP Josh Donaldson drove in a run and the Toronto Blue Jays defeated the Baltimore Orioles 4-3 Friday.

headline.print_headline: Martin Homers as Blue Jays Beat Orioles 4-3
